<C>__{ethan}
<D>__{stop callin' me 'uncle'... i ain't your uncle.}
<C>__{martin}
<D>__{yes, sir.}
<C>__{ethan}
<D>__{don't have to call me 'sir' neither... nor grampaw neither... nor methuselah neither... i can whup you to a frazzle.}
